Product Description

Whether you are wearing a formal suit or a casual dress this cherry coloured handbag from Bagsy Malone will not fail to add a stylish twist to your look. Featuring twin grab handles a zip fastening on the top and white stitch detailing on the front this handbag will win your heart at the very first look. Made from faux leather this handbag has an amazing finish and will last for years to come.
